message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with speech processing and recognition. cs.SD is followed by cs.SI (signal processing) and cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper discusses the use of an end-to-end learning method for audio source separation. cs.SD is also followed by cs.CL (computational linguistics) as the paper discusses the potential use of speech enhancement as a pre-processing step to speech recognition systems. Finally, cs.MM (multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with audio source separation in the context of music and speech.
